14854/scared-to-dance-be-pure-be-vigilant-behave-manic-street-preachers-q-a">在这里</a>获取门票。</p><p>他们还将<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/manic-street-preachers-suede-announce-joint-2024-uk-and-ireland-tour-dates-buy-tickets-3510432">与 Suede 一起进行英国和爱尔兰的联合巡演</a>，两支乐队轮流在每场演出的最后演奏。演出将于 6 月 28 日在兰戈伦国际音乐节 (Llangollen International Musical Eisteddfod) 拉开帷幕，并持续至 7 月 19 日在马盖特梦境 (Margate&#39;s Dreamland)。 <a href="https://ticketmaster-uk.tm7559.net/c/2862475/431519/7559?sharedid=NME&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ticketmaster.co.uk%2Fmanic-street-preachers-tickets%2Fartist%2F741429" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在这里</a>查找剩余的门票。</p><p>帖子<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/little-baby-nothings-new-manic-street-preachers-book-of-unseen-valerie-phillips-photos-announced-3767626">“小宝贝什么都没有”：新的狂躁街头传教士书籍中未公开的瓦莱丽·菲利普斯照片宣布</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
